F-150 Lightning</a>使用较小的电池可行驶 240 英里，而<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/rivian-r1t-electric-truck-review-150019762.html">Rivian R1T</a>可行驶 289 英里。这也远远低于 Lordstown 最初声称卡车可以行驶 250 英里的 EPA 额定值。</p><p>我们已征询洛兹敦的意见。 <em>Autoblog</em> <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.autoblog.com/2023/06/01/lordstown-endurance-pickup-gets-epa-rated-174-miles-of-range/?ncid=edlinkusauto00000015">指出</a>EPA 的数据有时过于保守。例如， <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-11-15-porsche-taycan-first-drive.html">保时捷 Taycan</a>在实际驾驶中经常超过政府规定的续航里程。 Endurance 的牵引力也超过 F-150，尽管它的有效载荷能力不到其一半。福特的售价也低了 399 美元。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>如果评级保持不变，它在很大程度上限制了 Endurance 对只需要短途运输的客户的吸引力，例如在一个城市不经常停靠的承包商。对于经常停靠的工人来说，这可能会有问题，更不用说那些必须在城市之间旅行的人了。</p><p>不管准确与否，EPA 评级加剧了洛兹敦的麻烦。俄亥俄品牌仍在<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/lordstown-motors-may-stop-endurance-ev-production-in-the-near-future-180630375.html">努力解决阻碍其产量的生产问题</a>。 <a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/gm-selling-its-stake-in-troubled-electric-pickup-maker-lordstown-motors-091509553.html">通用汽车去年出售了其在该公司的股份</a>，制造合作伙伴富士康威胁要退出涉嫌与股票相关的违约行为。现在，即使 Lordstown 能够解决其其他困境，Endurance 是否具有竞争力尚不清楚。</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/lordstowns-ev-pickup-has-a-worryingly-short-174-miles-of-epa-range-164714534.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/lordstowns-ev-pickup-has-a-worryingly-short-174-miles-of-epa-range-164714534.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 7227c373-8d86-4605-ac53-bfef63bea308</guid><dc:creator>乔恩·芬加斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Thu, 01 Jun 2023 16:47:14 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1685638040</ingested><modified> 2023-06-01T16:47:26+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Automotive Industry]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engad