国政府的 HMRC 应用进入 Wallet。由于这些卡片包含敏感信息，因此无论何时您想要使用它们，都必须通过手机登录（例如您的指纹）进行验证。今年晚些时候，您可以将公司徽章添加到 Wallet。</p><p>启用 RCS 后，您还可以通过 Google 的消息应用获取通行证。您可以使用聊天机器人登记航班或火车，并在不离开应用程序的情况下获得电子钱包通行证。这最初将通过西班牙火车运营商 Renfe 和越南航空公司提供给旅行者，而美食家可以通过 TagMe 等平台预订餐厅。</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/google-wallet-will-let-you-add-passes-by-taking-a-photo-160028725.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/google-wallet-will-let-you-add-passes-by-taking-a-photo-160028725.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 5686117c-a457-4bf1-bca6-18f92ad1529a</guid><dc:creator>乔恩·芬加斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Thu, 01 Jun 2023 16:00:28 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1685634640</ingested><modified> 2023-06-01T15:50:45+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Software]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Fingas]]></category><media:content height="1280" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/cef0aee0-008e-11ee-befd-cd61220f9a7e" width="1920"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1280" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/cef0aee0-008e-11ee-befd-cd61220f9a7e" width="1920"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Google]]></media:cred